metadata.description:
"Traveller ] [ i" is the first of the five pieces of the TRAVELLERS collection.

Go now, traveller, face this obstacleâ€¦


"We are travellers of our life, sometimes pioneers and sometimes lost wonderers.

In certain moments of our being, we will be alone, forced to face incomprehensible and frightening obstacles to overcome.

But there will always be the after, which will continue to send us a light, a promise of success.

And we, as living beings, must aim for that light, at any cost."
